{"tid":470972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫院很遠　請謹慎駕駛","createTime":"2017-11-16T23:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T02:55:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd536292eb54a73b2d074a680b618888758d4c72","tid":470972,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/16/realtime/4248746.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2Frealtime%2F4248746.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=4929900a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/16/realtime/4248747.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2Frealtime%2F4248747.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=74987cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/16/realtime/4248748.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2Frealtime%2F4248748.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=f2739a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/16/realtime/4248749.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2Frealtime%2F4248749.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=cfc276bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/16/realtime/4248750.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2Frealtime%2F4248750.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=4bd5d5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/16/realtime/4248751.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2Frealtime%2F4248751.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=7664390d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友在新竹西濱公路天府路口兩百公尺處，拍下有趣看板。圖／翻攝臉書社團新竹大小事<br />\n<br />\n今天有網友經過新竹南寮時，拍下電子看板的有趣標語，由於南寮位於海邊，鄰近沒有醫院，為了讓用路人小心駕駛，標語中提及「醫院很遠請謹慎駕駛」、「這附近沒有醫院請小心駕駛」、「天堂不遠 超速就到」、「酒後開車 死神上車」、「你若酒駕 我就改嫁」、「綠燈可以再等 生命不能重來」等標語，讓路過民眾在臉書上引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n「這不是胡鬧，是真的」，新竹市府交通處交通工程與管理科長林立偉表示，有別於過去呆板、冰冷的標語，在經過新竹道安會報後，由交通處同仁想出這些有趣的標語，並在十月份開始於竹市14個電子看板都能看到，希望以活潑、簡短又可以琅琅上口的標語，讓用路人看到時能夠「笑了之後還能有印象」，達到強化民眾對道路交通安全的重視與效果，也讓大小朋友能夠從生活中寓教於樂，從「人心」開始改變，並遵守交通安全規則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7324/2823046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7324%2F2823046&d=rMV4%2BPA%2FG49xNX6m63avIE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6327069b\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7324/2823046</a>"},{"pid":"2b401b5105e8d685c12c344e766081c3210a223f","tid":470972,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"<span sty